OL,3,CPromotion heartbreak for Rochdale in
OL,4,Cstoppage-time drama
OL,6,FRochdale have failed to clinch
OL,7,Fautomatic promotion back to the
OL,8,FFootball League after stoppage-time
OL,9,Fdrama saw two goals and a number of
OL,10,Ffan pitch invasions.
OL,12,FThe team needed to secure a win
OL,13,Fagainst rivals York City to pip them
OL,14,Fto the National League title, and
OL,15,Fafter a goalless game, scored scored
OL,16,Fthrough Emmanuel Dieseruvwe's header,
OL,17,Ffive minutes into added time.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
