CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777219865
OL,3,CPromotion heartbreak for Rochdale in
OL,4,Cstoppage-time drama
OL,6,FBut, after he rose to convert a cross
OL,7,Ffrom veteran Ian Henderson, it sparked
OL,8,Fa pitch invasion from home supporters
OL,9,Fat the Crown Oil Arena that delayed
OL,10,Fthe game for six minutes.
OL,12,FOnly six minutes added time had been
OL,13,Fput on the board but, by the time the
OL,14,Fgame restarted, it was the 103rd
OL,15,Fminute when York striker Stones
OL,16,Fequalised, with virtually the last
OL,17,Fkick of the game.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
