PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777219865
OL,3,CPromotion heartbreak for Rochdale in
OL,4,Cstoppage-time drama
OL,6,FHe forced the ball over the line in a
OL,7,Fterrific scramble after York threw 10
OL,8,Fplayers forward, a goal confirmed
OL,9,Fafter referee Will Finnie consulted
OL,10,Fhis watch and goal-line technology `
OL,11,Fsparking another pitch invasion, this
OL,12,Ftime by visiting fans.
OL,14,FRochdale could still go up in the play-
OL,15,Foffs and might have scored an earlier
OL,16,Finjury-time goal when York defender
OL,17,FCallum Howe headed Casey Pettit's
OL,18,Fcorner against his own crossbar.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777219865
OL,3,CPromotion heartbreak for Rochdale in
OL,4,Cstoppage-time drama
OL,6,FBut, after recording 108 points to win
OL,7,Fthe league, champions York have
OL,8,Fcompleted an impressive comeback,
OL,9,Fafter recently spending five seasons
OL,10,Fin the sixth-tier National League
OL,11,FNorth.
OL,13,FPrior to the game both clubs jointly
OL,14,Furged the football authorities to end
OL,15,Fthe "injustice" of only two teams
OL,16,Fbeing promoted from the National
OL,17,FLeague to the EFL each season.
OL,26,@wD@EOUwD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777219865
OL,3,CPromotion heartbreak for Rochdale in
OL,4,Cstoppage-time drama
OL,6,FThe clubs issued a joint statement 24
OL,7,Fhours before the game, insisting that
OL,8,Fboth supported the idea of '3UP'
OL,9,Fbetween the National League and League
OL,10,FTwo, regardless of Saturday's outcome.
OL,12,F"The National League is no longer a
OL,13,Fnon-league competition. It is
OL,14,Feffectively a League 3, with fully
OL,15,Fprofessional clubs operating at a
OL,16,Flevel equal to or higher than many of
OL,17,Fthose in League 2," the statement said.
OL,26,@tD@AOUyD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777219865
OL,3,CPromotion heartbreak for Rochdale in
OL,4,Cstoppage-time drama
OL,6,F"We both understand how important this
OL,7,Fgame is to both clubs and supporters.
OL,8,FWe both pledge now that whatever
OL,9,Fhappens tomorrow, we will both
OL,10,Fcontinue to fight for 3UP.
OL,12,F"Both clubs sit on over 100 points.
OL,13,FOne of us will have to fight once more
OL,14,Fin the National League play-offs.
OL,15,FHowever, we both strongly believe that
OL,16,Fthis shouldn't have to be the case.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777219865
OL,3,CPromotion heartbreak for Rochdale in
OL,4,Cstoppage-time drama
OL,6,F"We call on the National League,
OL,7,FFootball Regulator, EFL and Premier
OL,8,FLeague to come together immediately
OL,9,Fand resolve this issue, so that we do
OL,10,Fnot have to highlight this injustice
OL,11,Fyear after year."
OL,13,FThe 3UP campaign was launched in
OL,14,FFebruary 2025.
OL,16,FA spokesperson for the National League
OL,17,Fsaid: "Our 3UP campaign has gained the
OL,18,Foverwhelming support of fans, clubs,
OL,19,Forganisations and high-profile
OL,20,Ffootball names at every level of the
OL,21,Fgame.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@QO]yD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777219865
OL,3,CPromotion heartbreak for Rochdale in
OL,4,Cstoppage-time drama
OL,6,F"Additionally, it has generated
OL,7,Fsignificant media and political
OL,8,Fmomentum ` which has contributed to
OL,9,Fthe EFL formally debating the matter
OL,10,Fat their recent annual club meetings.
OL,12,F"We welcome this development and have
OL,13,Fsubsequently held follow-up
OL,14,Fconversations with the EFL as to the
OL,15,Fnext steps towards potential
OL,16,Fimplementation.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777219865
OL,3,CPromotion heartbreak for Rochdale in
OL,4,Cstoppage-time drama
OL,6,F"As the EFL has previously stated, 3UP
OL,7,Fwill require a vote of approval from
OL,8,Fthe majority of its clubs ` plus
OL,9,Fagreement between all parties on
OL,10,Frelated issues.
OL,12,F"We will work with the EFL to try and
OL,13,Fmake this happen on an appropriate and
OL,14,Foptimal timescale."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUvD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
